Global Electric Bus and Hybrid Bus Market Insights
Electric Bus and Hybrid Bus Market size was valued at USD 26.6 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 72.4 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 17.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Electric Bus and Hybrid Bus Market Overview
The Electric Bus and Hybrid Bus market is rapidly growing, with a projected market value reaching USD 67.89 billion by 2027, expanding at a CAGR of 18.1%. The transition to electric and hybrid buses is being driven by growing environmental concerns, governmental policies for cleaner transportation, and advancements in battery technologies. Electric buses are seen as a sustainable solution to reduce urban pollution and lower dependency on fossil fuels. This market is characterized by the increasing adoption of electric and hybrid bus technologies by public transport operators across the globe.

